metadata.description: Galactus is the terror of the universe, devouring planets and destroying civilizations as he goes -- and a father to a growing daughter! Meet GALI, daughter of the infamous planet-eater GALACTUS! Unlike her father, Gali has formed an affection for the planet Earth, and does her best to subsist only on invasive alien life-forms...but when her cosmic hunger begins growing out of control, can she hold herself back from a deadly binge? Featuring WOLVERINE, THOR, and the FANTASTIC FOUR!
metadata.name: Galacta: Daughter of Galactus
